q_en: Send 1000 Leathers to the Main Warehouse for storage.
thought: First, we need to identify the ID of the material 'Leather' from the materials table. Then, we need to check the ID of 'Main Warehouse' from the warehouse table. Finally, we will insert the material into the warehouse_material table with the specified quantity (1000).

sqls.command: SELECT id FROM materials WHERE name = 'Leather';SELECT id FROM warehouse WHERE name = 'Main Warehouse';INSERT INTO warehouse_material (id, warehouse_id, material_id, left_number) VALUES (UUID(), (SELECT id FROM warehouse WHERE name = 'Main Warehouse'), (SELECT id FROM materials WHERE name = 'Leather'), 1000);
